{% comment %}
  Shared Yotpo star-rating widget — the single source of truth for the
  per-product rating stars (product cards + PDP header). Emits the Yotpo
  star-ratings widget instance div; the per-store loader
  (snippets/yotpo-loader) hydrates every `.yotpo-widget-instance` on the
  page, so any template rendering this snippet must also
  `{% render 'yotpo-loader' %}` once.

  Self-gated on the reviews flag + a SKU — renders nothing otherwise, so
  callers may include it unconditionally.

  Params:
    sku   product SKU — Yotpo's per-product identifier (required)
{% endcomment %}
{% if settings.aico_reviews_enabled and sku and sku != '' %}
  <div class="yotpo-widget-instance" data-yotpo-instance-id="{{ settings.aico_yotpo_widget_instance_id }}" data-yotpo-product-id="{{ sku }}"></div>
{% endif %}
